    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371570/extras/e7b8cbf438a6b67aa3168fd20379672e.avif?t=1770745500\" width=614 height=249 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371570/extras/369b863b5e236f5f2be3f4703ea2d6f4.webp?t=1770745500\" width=18 height=18 /></span>  欢迎来到首款木偶戏 RPG！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371570/extras/478dade6befd3d0649f8274f058a5180.webp?t=1770745500\" width=18 height=18 /></span>  对抗海量敌人，提升各种等级，施放魔法并招募新英雄。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371570/extras/045c76fb5de4db43b5203ff25ed7c6a6.webp?t=1770745500\" width=18 height=18 /></span>  或者坐下来放松一下，或者去做点别的事情，让你的英雄自行去战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371570/extras/236bc5a90f84f91c903e5a5d6b9547ad.webp?t=1770745500\" width=18 height=18 /></span>  不过切记，你需要确保你的英雄足够强大，才能放手让他们自己去战斗，尤其是要面对头目的时候！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371570/extras/733c918eef6d032ae99801683fe28d66.webp?t=1770745500\" width=18 height=18 /></span>  尽情享受吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371570/extras/bc84e8bb2c4e5e47f60d7632a958f5af.avif?t=1770745500\" width=576 height=180 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70 余种不同的敌人和头目</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 个不同的区域</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一群特别的英雄，各有不同的能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对敌人施放有趣的能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合了 RPG 和点击刷刷刷地元素，还有海量可升级的技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绝无任何形式的微交易</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大概是无尽玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >木偶戏舞台画面，上面还有一群可爱的木偶英雄！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371570/extras/Bosses.PNG?t=1770745500\" /></span></p>",
